data.description: STEP INSIDE and be surprised at what this 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch has to offer you. With tons of natural sunlight, a country kitchen, quaint dining area, cozy living room, and a rocking chair front porch. This home is nestled on just over 10 acres of land, approx 7 acres of which is wooded. There is an 40 x 30, insulated pole barn, with propane heat, 100 amp service, 2 overhead doors, 1 sliding door, concrete floor, with work benches, and shelves. This property is located just a quick hour from Indianapolis International Airport, 30 minutes from Bloomington, and 15 minutes from Spencer. The pride of ownership and attention to detail will put every other house you've seen, at this price, to shame. It's a must see inside and out.
